                <div id="bootstrap-panel--11--content" class="panel-body panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div id="Recommendations of Others" class="field field--name-field-preface field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item table-responsive">
                       <p>Currently, no professional organizations in the US recommend clinical visual examination for skin cancer screening. Although the American Academy of Dermatology does not have formal guidelines on clinician-performed skin cancer screening, it does encourage and provide resources for its clinician members to hold free skin cancer screening events for the public.<sup><a href="#citation8">8</a>,<a href="#citation28">28</a></sup></p>
